    "about": {
        "title": "Family Winery Putec Vinosady | About Us",
        "imagePath": "/o-nas/rodina1.JPG",
        "content": "Putec s.r.o. is a family winery with a long-standing tradition in Vinosady near Pezinok, specializing in the production of premium wines and offering accommodation and wine tastings.\n\nOur history began with a passion for viticulture and a desire to create something unique. Today, we are known for our meticulous approach to winemaking and our personal relationship with customers from Bratislava, Senec, Trnava, and the entire region.\n\nWe believe in the power of tradition, the value of quality ingredients, and the joy of sharing great wines with the community. Every bottle is chosen with love - and every customer becomes part of our extended family. We offer accommodation and wine tastings in the beautiful surroundings of Vinosady."
